bilingual.source: He also does a typical Sunday roast.
bilingual.target: 他还会做典型的周日烤肉。

bilingual.source: He also can make a typical Sunday roast.
bilingual.target: 他也能做一顿典型的周日烤肉。

bilingual.source: The Taylors are a typical American family.
bilingual.target: 泰勒一家是一个典型的美国家庭。

bilingual.source: To cheer her up, we went to a typical Quebec restaurant for lunch.
bilingual.target: 为了让她高兴起来，我们去了一家典型的魁北克餐馆吃午饭。

bilingual.source: Some typical themes of Chinese New Year paintings are folk tales and gods.
bilingual.target: 一些典型的中国新年画主题是民间故事和神灵。

bilingual.source: One example is the typical Chinese Spring Festival custom of lighting firecrackers.
bilingual.target: 一个例子是典型的中国春节放鞭炮的习俗。

yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么？出什么事了？典型的狗屁官僚主义。

yingyinNormal.en: In typical Bass man fashion, his pursuit was direct, and at times, not exactly subtle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他是典型的拜斯家族男人，追求直接，并不是那么的精心追求。

yingyinNormal.en: Blah, blah, blah. typical Taurus. So, seriously. are we going to see you Saturday? I don't think so.
yingyinNormal.zh: 叽里呱啦叽里呱啦，典型的金牛座，说真的，我们是不是周六见？我想不是吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, this is a typical lightning-bearer thing. Right there, it's like, 'Hello, who wants one of my phallic-shaped man-cakes?'
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是典型的闪电使者行为。就像是“嗨，谁要来一根我的阴茎形状的蛋糕？”

yingyinNormal.en: But while our businesses are creating jobs at the fastest pace since the 90s, the typical family hasn't seen a raise since the 90s also.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但当我们的经济自90年代以来以最快的速度创造着就业岗位，一个典型的家庭却自90年代以来从未看到工资的上涨。

yingyinNormal.en: Because even though corporate profits and the stock market have hit all-time highs the typical family isn't bringing home more than they did 15 years ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为即便企业利润和股票市场已经冲到历史性高度，典型的家庭在生活中并没有比15年前过得更好。

yingyinNormal.en: A typical trip, Miami to Tampa, Tampa to Houston, Houston to Vegas, Vegas to Houston, Houston to Dallas, Dallas to Tokyo, Tokyo to Hong kong, Hong kong to Macau. Thanks, boss.
yingyinNormal.zh: 典型的旅途，迈阿密到坦帕市，然后再去休斯顿，休斯顿到维加斯，维加斯到休斯顿休斯顿到达拉斯 达拉斯到东京，东京到香港，香港到澳门。谢谢老板。

yingyinNormal.en: Which suggests either a remarkable passivity among the, I assume, 24 to 36 residents of this building, based on the number of mailboxes and given typical urban population density or a shared delusion of functionality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就说明要么这楼的24到36户人家，我假设的，基于邮箱的个数和典型的城市人口密度得出的都特别懒散，要么都同时产生功能性错觉。

yingyinNormal.en: Typical Christmassy stuff, you know. Our holidays are pretty traditional.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一般的圣诞节活动，你知道的，我们过节的方式是很传统的。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, they're all up there, huh? Hmm, typical. It's axiomatically atypical.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们都在楼上，是吗？正常。这很明显不正常。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, please, that is such a lame excuse. I mean, that's a typical guy response.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，这个借口真烂，男生都是这种反应。

yingyinNormal.en: It needs to decide is this person's behavior typical or is it out of the ordinary?
yingyinNormal.zh: 大脑需要决定这个人的行为合乎常理吗？还是违背常理？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, looks like it. These aren't you typical spring pre-hillbillies. These guys are pros.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，应该是的，这些人可不是乱打一气的乡巴佬，都是专业的。

yingyinNormal.en: Typical. Tea. We did not communicate through mere words. Our souls met. Precisely. My soul and the prince's soul.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真独特。茶。我们不需用言语交流，我们的灵魂相遇了。准确的说，我的灵魂和王子的灵魂。

yingyinNormal.en: I did your horoscope, remember? I was going to do everybody's, until Sheldon went on one of his typical psychotic rants.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我占卜过你的星座，还记得？我还想占卜你们每一个的，直到被谢尔顿那典型且神经兮兮的理论所打断。

yingyinNormal.en: Literally, we put a GPS unit on a pizza delivery man and recorded his typical Friday night in the heart of New York city.
yingyinNormal.zh: 简单来说，我们在一个披萨送货员身上放了一个定位仪来记录下他在一个普通的周末夜晚。

yingyinNormal.en: The typical American with a bachelor's degree or higher earns over $28,000 more per year than someone with just a high school diploma.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拥有本科学历的普通美国人每年的收入要比那些只有高中学历的人的收入高2.8万美元。

yingyinNormal.en: They never went upstairs to visit the former tenants, so your characterization of their behavior as typical is demonstrably fallacious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 以前他们从不上楼拜访房客，而你将他们的行为鉴定为正常是绝对的谬误。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Saito, this isn't your typical corporate espionage. You asked me for inception. I do hope you understand the gravity of that request.
yingyinNormal.zh: 齐藤先生，这不是你常用的商业间谍手段，是你要求我植入意念，你要明白实行要求的后果。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
